
-- =============================================================================
-- QUID COMPANY TERMINAL
-- CompanyTerminal
--
-- Clean company registration client for the Quid banking system.
-- Mouse-only navigation. Keyboard only edits the selected input field.
--
-- Flow:
--   1. User logs in with normal citizen bank details
--   2. Company registration uses that logged-in citizen_id as owner_id
--   3. ServerSideAccounts creates company:<ticker> as a separate bank account
--
-- Requires existing ServerSideAccounts handlers:
--   login, register_company, company_info
-- =============================================================================

